description.p:
1.


In SiteCreator, copy, rename, and modify the Area Spec and Workflow Spec documents for an existing area;


2.


Add the new area name to the Area Spec for every area that should internavigate with the new area;


3.


Copy and modify the Area Profile and Workflow Profile documents that correspond to the new Spec documents;


4.


Add the new area name to the Site Spec and FileUpload Spec documents;


5.


Refresh the affected Spec, Profile, and File Upload documents; and


6.


Upload the navigation graphics for the new area into the Library.
